data.description:
UPDATED SINGLE FAMILY HOME partially built  1970s (original 1/3 structure 1933) offers privacy, situated within end-of-lane cul-de-sac.  Located minutes from GEICO, easily accessible to downtown Macon and interstate. 
UPDATES to This LARGE home include NEWER (recently replaced) ROOF, WINDOWS, HOT WATER HEATER, FLOORING, KITCHEN cabinets and countertops, and BRAND NEW HVAC. Home also features tall ceilings, good size rooms, open kitchen, granite countertops, laminate flooring separate laundry room, garage, fenced yard.
Appointment ONLY to view. Owned by licensed agent.
